'''Afus''' ɣer [[afgan|ufgan]] d [[agman]] gar yegmanen ifellayen, yezga-d deg taggara n [[Iɣil|yiɣil]]. Yal afgan ɣur-s sin  n ifassen, '''afus ayfus''' akked '''ufus aẓelmaṭ''', yal afus ɣur-s semmus (5) n [[Aḍad|iṭudan]] d [[idikel]], s yessen yezmer ufgan ad yeg aṭas n tigawin (ad yeṭṭef, ad yaru ...) neɣ ad t-issexdem deg  [[tutlayt n izmal]]. Afus d allal ilan (yesɛan) azal ameqran ɣer ufgan.

== [[Iɣess|iɣsan]] n ufus ==

== Ifassen ɣer iɣersiwen ==

==Tamawalt==
Addad amaruz : Ufus<br>
Asget : Ifassen

==Aseqdec==
Yesseqdac umdan ifassen-is aṭas deg tudert-is n yal ass, gar tigawin i yezmer ad yeg ufus : Arfad n tɣawsiwin (tudma), tuṭfa, tira, aktili, učči, atg. 

==Aglam n ufus==
[[File:Human palm with numbers.jpg|upright|thumb|Afus aẓelmaḍ]]
Afus d aḥric aneggaru deg yiɣil, deg-s tidikelt, ɣur-s cudden-d semmus (5) n yiḍudan :<br>
# Adebbuz
# Uskin : Yezga-d gar udebbuz d uḍad ameqran
# Aḍad ameqran : D netta i d ameqran akk gar yiḍudan.
# Warisem : Yezga-d gar uḍad ameqran d umeẓyan.
# Aḍad ameẓyan : D netta i d ameẓyan akk gar yiḍudan.

==Taɣessa (Squelette)==
Afus n umdan amengaḍ (adulte) ɣur-s snat n tmarwin ṣa (27) n yiɣsan, bḍan ɣef kraḍ (3) n yeḥricen : acaṛuf, timceḍt n ufus akked tɣessa n yiḍudan.<br>
Acaṛuf ɣur-s ṭam (8) n yiɣsan imeẓyanen, timceḍt n ufus ɣur-s semmus (5) n yiɣsan ma d taɣessa n yiḍudan ɣur-s mraw kuẓ (14) n yiɣsan iɣezfanen.

